				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">things like this are often just opinionated assumptions.
<br />

<br />
comparing a mage to a wizard, IMO, is just like comparing a paladin to a warrior.  granted equipment, the warrior is just going ot have more hp/ac than the pally, because that is HIS ROLE.
<br />

<br />
Wizards ARE the masters of nuking power, period.  saying they get ports making them more powerful than a mage is kind of pointless.. i mean serious do you feel like porting people around all day?
<br />

<br />
Root/snare- come on, if we had root/snare mages WOULD be the powerhouse of eq.  I personally see no reason for a mage to need root or snare.
<br />

<br />
Absorb damage: /shrug this is one aspect i have always argued for, considering chanters, wizzies and necros all get a rune, and mages do not, i feel that part is unbalanced, but in any given raid situation/group situation, i only ever seem to get hit if: 1. some mob spawns out of no where and i was sitting. 2. i over nuke and get aggro.  both of which if i were paying attention more often i would not be getting hit anyway, so to me a rune is not that important (minus mobs with AoE spells, but then i do not think i would want to just sit there and re-cast my rune over and over...)
<br />

<br />
buffs:  mages and wizzies get the same line of resist buffs as far as i know. minus their familiars which help, but so /shrug that is what a wizard is.  they cannot summon mod rods, we can, that is why we are mages.
<br />

<br />
As far as damage and speed of spells, well again that is why they are a wizard, and we are mages.  
<br />

<br />
conclusion,  do not underestimate your pet.. or your damage shield..  if you actually parsed out your pets damage, plus the damage inflicted with your damage shield, plus your spells, i think you would be very impressed with the results.  If i had the choice to go back and start over having a level 65 wizzy or a 65 mage, i would still stick to the mage, so i do not have a 6k crit /shrug,  wizards don have a pet that can rampage and flurry ^_~<br />_________________<br />Sage Akito Tenkawa
