<br />

<br />
We have our value to raids..so-so dps ( do not include pets since half the time they are not allowed) T-rods, focus items, arrows, DS.
<br />

<br />
Yes we need something changed to increase our DPS on raids and yes we fall way short when it come to the "well they have a pet" thing. 
<br />

<br />
Truth be told our pet is not readily accesible. It's not there on alot of raids and it is not there if we are running through a hostile zone and a see invis mob attacks.
<br />

<br />
Make our pets a extreamly fast cast time then I could agree with SoE about not having  root/snare / any means of holding off the enemy. Until then we are and always will be handcuffed.
